track.name: All the Way
comments: it's no good unless he needs you all the way~
The Joker Is Wild Good Movie Great Song
SINATRA,THERE NO MORE TO SAID! LOVE YOU FRANK.

Saw him twice.  First time as an early 20 something with my Mom and her Mom and what an experience; three generations of women swooning over him.  Second time was at his opening of our area's first huge scale entertainment arena with the man I would marry on one of our earlier dates. Great time all around.

This is how it was and it's PERFECT!  Remember when they had to get it right in one take and it wasn't done in tracks but with the audience, the piano play and the singer all in one room?  This is what this is, it's history.  Anyone can lift a vocal track and lay it over background music but to get it right in one try,  THAT is artistry.  We need more of this, more recordings from 78 RPM records with all of the buzz, pop and hiss that went with it.
The audio quality of this track is awful.  What's up, last.fm?
